  "privacyTitle": "Don't Forget! — Privacy Policy",
  "privacyIntro": "This Privacy Policy describes how the \"Don't Forget!\" app handles your personal data. Please read carefully.",
  "privacyDataTitle": "1. Data Collected",
  "privacyDataBody": "The app does NOT collect any personal data on its own servers. All data you enter (shopping lists, items, prices) is stored exclusively:\n\n• In your device's local storage (Hive/SQLite).\n• In your own Google Drive (private app folder), if you choose to enable backup.",
  "privacyDriveTitle": "2. Google Drive and Google Sign-In",
  "privacyDriveBody": "If you choose to back up, the app will request access to your Google account with the \"drive.appdata\" scope. This scope allows saving files only in the hidden, private app folder on your Google Drive.\n\nNo other data from your Google account is accessed. Backup files are not visible in the normal Google Drive interface.",
  "privacySharingTitle": "3. Data Sharing",
  "privacySharingBody": "The app does NOT share your data with third parties. List sharing codes are generated locally on your device and travel only through the channels you choose (WhatsApp, SMS, email, etc.).",
  "privacyStorageTitle": "4. Storage and Security",
  "privacyStorageBody": "Your data is under your exclusive control:\n\n• Local data: stored on your device.\n• Backup: in your Google Drive account, protected by Google's security policies.\n\nWe do not have access to, nor the ability to access, your personal data.",
  "privacyDeleteTitle": "5. Data Deletion",
  "privacyDeleteBody": "To delete your data:\n\n• Local data: uninstall the app.\n• Drive backup: go to drive.google.com/drive/appdata and delete the file \"nao_esquece_backup.json\".",
  "privacyChangesTitle": "6. Changes to this Policy",
  "privacyChangesBody": "We may update this policy periodically. Relevant updates will be communicated within the app itself.",
  "privacyContactTitle": "7. Contact",
  "privacyContactBody": "Questions about privacy? Contact us via the email listed on the app's Play Store page.",
  "privacyLastUpdate": "Last updated: March 2026",

